00:13:36,783 --> 00:13:37,917
( Noriaki gasps )

251
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,823
Jotaro: I have zero intention
of hurting her.

252
00:13:42,856 --> 00:13:44,624
Heh.

253
00:13:44,658 --> 00:13:46,360
Now that i’ve dragged it out,

254
00:13:46,393 --> 00:13:49,563
I see it for what it is,
just a sleazy stand

255
00:13:49,596 --> 00:13:51,565
whose only ability
is to possess people.

256
00:13:51,598 --> 00:13:53,366
- ( Teeth crunch )
- ( Noriaki winces )

257
00:13:56,503 --> 00:13:59,906
Jotaro: So this is
your stand, kakyoin?

258
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:03,277
This green, stripy thing
looks like shiny melon.

259
00:14:04,545 --> 00:14:06,580
Noriaki: You’re
gonna regret doing that.

260
00:14:06,613 --> 00:14:09,616
Dragging that out of her
was a mistake, jojo.

261
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:10,618
( Yells )

262
00:14:10,651 --> 00:14:12,753
Jotaro: Don’t act tough.

263
00:14:12,786 --> 00:14:15,489
I can see my finger marks
on your forehead.

264
00:14:15,522 --> 00:14:16,723
( Spits )

265
00:14:16,757 --> 00:14:19,260
If I decide to crush
your stand’s head

266
00:14:19,293 --> 00:14:20,795
like the melon it is,

267
00:14:20,828 --> 00:14:23,431
then i’m guessin’
your head’ll get crushed, too.

268
00:14:24,464 --> 00:14:25,865
( Noriaki gagging )

269
00:14:25,899 --> 00:14:28,568
Jotaro: I’m gonna keep
a tight grip on you for now.

270
00:14:28,602 --> 00:14:30,637
We’re gonna pay my gramps
a little visit.

271
00:14:30,671 --> 00:14:32,840
I’m sure he’d love
to meet you...

272
00:14:34,374 --> 00:14:37,677
And i’d like to know
more about dio myself.

273
00:14:40,047 --> 00:14:41,382
( Jotaro gasps )

274
00:14:42,449 --> 00:14:44,384
♪

275
00:14:44,418 --> 00:14:46,020
What the hell?

276
00:14:46,053 --> 00:14:49,490
What’s that green liquid
coming out of his stand’s hand?

277
00:14:49,523 --> 00:14:51,492
Noriaki: You should
have listened, jojo.

278
00:14:51,525 --> 00:14:54,962
I told you you’re
gonna regret this, didn’t I?

279
00:14:54,995 --> 00:14:58,499
This is the attack of my stand,
hierophant green.

280
00:14:58,532 --> 00:15:00,868
Jotaro: No weird moves, kakyoin!

281
00:15:00,901 --> 00:15:02,903
♪

282
00:15:08,709 --> 00:15:11,478
Noriaki: Emerald splash!

283
00:15:12,479 --> 00:15:13,880
( Stand yells )

284
00:15:21,822 --> 00:15:23,657
♪

285
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:25,392
Noriaki: So what do you think?

286
00:15:25,425 --> 00:15:27,761
Did you like emerald splash?

287
00:15:27,794 --> 00:15:30,430
That fluid you saw
in hierophant green

288
00:15:30,464 --> 00:15:33,033
is actually
a surge of destructive energy.

289
00:15:33,066 --> 00:15:36,002
It tore straight
though your stand’s chest,

290
00:15:36,036 --> 00:15:39,306
and your insides
have now been torn to shreds.

291
00:15:39,339 --> 00:15:42,475
And as for
that doctor over there...

292
00:15:42,509 --> 00:15:44,478
( Bones cracking )

293
00:15:45,646 --> 00:15:46,981
Jotaro: Why?

294
00:15:47,014 --> 00:15:50,684
I know I took that stand
out of her, so how?

295
00:15:50,717 --> 00:15:52,419
Noriaki: I told you already,

296
00:15:52,452 --> 00:15:54,421
but let me reiterate.

297
00:15:54,454 --> 00:15:56,389
I tried to warn you
that by attacking

298
00:15:56,423 --> 00:15:59,326
my hierophant green,
it would hurt her as well.

299
00:15:59,359 --> 00:16:01,628
My stand can travel
farther than yours,

300
00:16:01,662 --> 00:16:03,864
but it dislikes open spaces.

301
00:16:03,897 --> 00:16:07,901
Without exception, it prefers
to hide within something.

302
00:16:07,935 --> 00:16:11,639
If you drag it out,
it gets angry.

303
00:16:11,672 --> 00:16:14,909
That’s why, when you
ripped it out of her throat,

304
00:16:14,942 --> 00:16:17,011
it hurt her along the way.

305
00:16:17,044 --> 00:16:18,679
You’re the one
who did this to her.

306
00:16:18,712 --> 00:16:20,781
This is entirely
your fault, jojo.

307
00:16:20,814 --> 00:16:22,983
You must be held responsible.

308
00:16:23,016 --> 00:16:24,784
Look at what you’ve done.

309
00:16:24,818 --> 00:16:27,688
All you had to do
was let me kill you,

310
00:16:27,721 --> 00:16:29,990
and the doctor would have
walked away unharmed.

311
00:16:31,091 --> 00:16:33,093
♪

312
00:16:34,394 --> 00:16:36,062
And still you get up.

313
00:16:36,096 --> 00:16:38,031
You are so pathetic.

314
00:16:38,065 --> 00:16:40,034
You’re nothing more
than a sandbag

315
00:16:40,067 --> 00:16:43,470
about to be pummeled
by a skilled boxer.

316
00:16:43,504 --> 00:16:44,905
Why even bother standing up?

317
00:16:44,938 --> 00:16:47,474
I’m just gonna
knock you down again.

318
00:16:50,711 --> 00:16:52,046
Jotaro: Look...

319
00:16:52,079 --> 00:16:55,516
No one ever said
jotaro kujo was a nice guy.

320
00:16:55,549 --> 00:16:56,884
♪

321
00:16:56,917 --> 00:17:00,087
I beat the crap out of people
more than I have to.

322
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:03,156
Some are even
still in the hospital.

323
00:17:03,190 --> 00:17:05,859
I’ve had idiot teachers
who liked to talk big,

324
00:17:05,893 --> 00:17:09,497
so I taught them a lesson, and
they never came back to class.

325
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:12,933
If I go to a restaurant
and the food’s bad,

326
00:17:12,966 --> 00:17:16,570
I make it a policy
to stiff ’em with the bill.

327
00:17:16,603 --> 00:17:20,674
But even a bastard like me

328
00:17:20,707 --> 00:17:23,577
can spot true evil
when he sees it.

329
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:27,714
True evil are those who use
the weak for their own gain,

330
00:17:27,748 --> 00:17:30,084
then crush them underfoot
when they’re through...

331
00:17:31,518 --> 00:17:34,488
Especially an innocent woman.

332
00:17:34,521 --> 00:17:37,591
And that is exactly
what you’ve done, isn’t it?

333
00:17:37,624 --> 00:17:40,627
And your stand
gets to hide from the victim,

334
00:17:40,661 --> 00:17:42,897
the law, and the consequences.

335
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:44,899
That’s why...

336
00:17:44,932 --> 00:17:47,201
I will judge you myself.

337
00:17:47,234 --> 00:17:48,669
Noriaki: I’m evil?

338
00:17:48,702 --> 00:17:50,204
See, that’s where you’re wrong.

339
00:17:50,237 --> 00:17:52,706
Evil is always the loser.

340
00:17:52,739 --> 00:17:54,808
It’s the Victor who has justice,

341
00:17:54,842 --> 00:17:57,211
the Victor being
the last man standing.

342
00:17:57,244 --> 00:18:00,614
And how you win in battle
is irrelevant!

343
00:18:00,647 --> 00:18:02,149
♪

344
00:18:10,224 --> 00:18:12,993
See, the loser
is always the evil one.

345
00:18:13,026 --> 00:18:15,695
Time to finish you off.

346
00:18:15,729 --> 00:18:18,599
Jotaro: Really?
The loser’s evil?

347
00:18:18,632 --> 00:18:22,936
Noriaki: Emerald splash!

348
00:18:22,970 --> 00:18:25,573
Jotaro: Then, let me show you...

349
00:18:27,174 --> 00:18:28,842
- ( Stand roars )
- Noriaki: What?

350
00:18:28,876 --> 00:18:30,745
There’s no way.

351
00:18:30,777 --> 00:18:32,746
No one can just deflect
the emerald splash.

352
00:18:32,779 --> 00:18:35,148
Jotaro:
...Just how evil you are.

353
00:18:36,149 --> 00:18:38,918
( Stand yelling )

354
00:18:38,952 --> 00:18:40,921
( Noriaki gags )

355
00:18:43,891 --> 00:18:45,693
Stand: Ora!

356
00:18:48,829 --> 00:18:50,831
( Yelling )

357
00:18:52,266 --> 00:18:54,769
Jotaro: I’ll teach you justice

358
00:18:54,801 --> 00:18:56,770
with my stand!

359
00:18:59,973 --> 00:19:01,541
( Class screaming )

360
00:19:01,575 --> 00:19:04,144
( Noriaki screams )

361
00:19:04,178 --> 00:19:07,581
Your stand has incredible power.

362
00:19:08,815 --> 00:19:10,884
Jotaro: You caught me
by surprise earlier

363
00:19:10,918 --> 00:19:12,787
and scratched its chest
a little.

364
00:19:12,819 --> 00:19:15,088
I’m glad my stand isn’t weak,

365
00:19:15,122 --> 00:19:19,760
but sometimes it feels like it
can get more savage than I am.

366
00:19:19,793 --> 00:19:21,828
That was a close call.

367
00:19:24,832 --> 00:19:27,201
She’ll be fine
once her wounds are treated.

368
00:19:27,234 --> 00:19:28,602
- ( School bell rings )
- Hmm?

369
00:19:28,635 --> 00:19:30,103
Boy: Did a gas pipe just burst?

370
00:19:30,137 --> 00:19:31,939
Boy #2: It came
from the doctor’s office.

371
00:19:31,972 --> 00:19:33,240
Man: Everyone,
stay in the classroom!

372
00:19:33,273 --> 00:19:35,008
Jotaro: I’ll leave
the cleanup to them.

373
00:19:35,042 --> 00:19:37,878
I’ve had enough school
for one day.

374
00:19:37,911 --> 00:19:39,613
This guy needs to talk.

375
00:19:39,646 --> 00:19:42,182
I wanna hear
everything he knows about dio.

376
00:19:42,216 --> 00:19:44,218
♪

377
00:19:55,896 --> 00:19:57,898
( Holly humming a tune )

378
00:20:01,835 --> 00:20:02,869
( Gasps )

379
00:20:04,204 --> 00:20:07,007
( Footsteps )

380
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:09,175
I just had
the most amazing connection

381
00:20:09,209 --> 00:20:10,911
with my son right now.

382
00:20:10,944 --> 00:20:14,014
Jotaro must be thinking about me
at school this very second.

383
00:20:14,047 --> 00:20:15,682
Jotaro: I’m not
thinking about you.

384
00:20:15,716 --> 00:20:18,219
( Holly yelps )
Jotaro!

385
00:20:18,252 --> 00:20:19,854
Why aren’t you at school?

386
00:20:19,887 --> 00:20:22,223
And who is that boy
on your shoulder?

387
00:20:22,256 --> 00:20:24,592
Is that blood
that he’s covered in?

388
00:20:24,625 --> 00:20:27,962
Wait a sec. Please don’t
tell me you did that.

389
00:20:27,995 --> 00:20:30,130
Jotaro: None of your business.

390
00:20:30,164 --> 00:20:32,933
I need to find the old man.

391
00:20:32,966 --> 00:20:36,002
Finding someone
in this big house really sucks.

392
00:20:36,036 --> 00:20:39,006
Holly: I think you can find him
with avdol right now.

393
00:20:39,039 --> 00:20:40,274
They’re both in the tea room.

394
00:20:40,307 --> 00:20:42,876
♪

395
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:47,281
Oh, jotaro,
you never tell me anything.

396
00:20:47,314 --> 00:20:52,653
All that does is make me worry
about you all the time.

397
00:20:52,686 --> 00:20:54,988
But still,
I know that, deep down,

398
00:20:55,022 --> 00:20:56,790
you really do mean well.

399
00:20:56,823 --> 00:20:59,326
You’re a very sweet little boy
at heart.

400
00:20:59,359 --> 00:21:01,328
- Jotaro: Hey.
- Holly: Yes?

401
00:21:01,361 --> 00:21:05,665
Jotaro: You’re lookin’
a little bit pale the morning.

402
00:21:05,699 --> 00:21:06,833
You all right?

403
00:21:06,867 --> 00:21:09,770
( Holly gasps )

404
00:21:09,803 --> 00:21:10,771
Yay!

405
00:21:10,804 --> 00:21:13,674
I’m fine! Thank you!

406
00:21:13,707 --> 00:21:14,975
( Jotaro scoffs )

407
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:17,878
Holly: I knew it.

408
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:23,050
Joseph: Well, I hate to say it,
but it’s too late for him.

409
00:21:23,083 --> 00:21:25,352
There’s no way he’ll make it.

410
00:21:25,385 --> 00:21:28,855
He’s got a few days
before he dies at most.

411
00:21:28,889 --> 00:21:31,959
Jotaro, this is not your fault.
Trust me.

412
00:21:31,992 --> 00:21:35,429
Do you want to know why this man
swore his allegiance to dio

413
00:21:35,462 --> 00:21:38,298
and came to your school
to kill you?

414
00:21:38,332 --> 00:21:41,368
Look right here,
and I will show you!

415
00:21:43,904 --> 00:21:45,806
Jotaro: What the hell is that?

416
00:21:48,242 --> 00:21:50,244
♪

